<ex>chass⟦eacute⟧</ex>; <ex>chass⟦eacute⟧</ex> to the right or
left</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chasse</ent>⟦br⟧
